---
---

<section class="problem section" aria-labelledby="problem-heading">
	<div class="container">
		<h2 id="problem-heading" class="problem__heading">
			You did the work. Now comes the chase.
		</h2>
		<p class="problem__body">
			The job's done, the crew's moved on, and you're still waiting to get
			paid. So you dig up photos, hunt down compliance docs, and chase the GC
			with call after call — doing a second job just to collect on the first.
			Every week you wait is money sitting in someone else's account instead of
			yours.
		</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.problem {
		background: var(--color-surface);
		border-block: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.problem__heading {
		font-size: clamp(1.625rem, 4.5vw, 2.5rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: -0.015em;
		line-height: 1.15;
		max-width: 20ch;
	}

	.problem__body {
		margin-top: 1.25rem;
		font-size: clamp(1.0625rem, 2.2vw, 1.25rem);
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		max-width: 60ch;
	}
</style>
